{"id":301086221,"lang":"python","time":"1 year, 5 months","timestamp":1581091368,"status_display":"Time Limit Exceeded","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/301086221/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"3Sum","memory":"N/A","code":"from collections import defaultdict\nclass Solution:\n    def threeSum(self, nums):\n        d = defaultdict(list)\n        N = len(nums)\n        for i in range(N):\n            for j in range(N):\n                if i == j:\n                    continue\n                key = 0 - nums[i] - nums[j]\n                d[key].append([i, j])\n        \n        ans_set = set()\n        for i in range(N):\n            key = nums[i]\n            for item in d[key]:\n                idx_list = [i] + item\n                if len(set(idx_list)) == 3:\n                    val_list = sorted([nums[idx] for idx in idx_list])\n                    ans_set.add(tuple(val_list))\n        \n        ans_list = [list(item) for item in ans_set]\n        return ans_list\n\n","compare_result":"","title_slug":"3sum"}
